title: [Head Over Heels, Cordwainers]
description: The room has been set up to serve as a showcase of the goods available within.  Glass topped cases and gilded racks have been filled with pairs of boots and slippers, all of different design.  Satin-trimmed banners over the arches at the back of the room depict a boldly outlined slipper and a stylized boot.  One wall is hung with a framed sign.

Set back in a small alcove, the shop is crammed with Glass topped cases, carved mistwood boxes, and gilded racks.  Each display is filled with various materials for creating all manner of footware.  Satin-trimmed banners over a a pair of openings at the back of the room depict a boldly outlined slipper and a stylized boot.  A small framed sign is hung over a low polished table.
